data.description: Introducing an incredible opportunity for savvy buyers! This 2-story home is awaiting your personal touch and cosmetic renovation. The best part? Renovation financing is available, making it easier than ever to turn this diamond in the rough into your dream home. With an estimated $25,000 to $35,000 in upgrades/repairs needed, you have the flexibility to transform this property into a true masterpiece. Imagine selecting the perfect flooring to enhance each room and adding a fresh coat of paint to breathe new life into both the interior and exterior. Let your creativity run wild as you envision the possibilities! One standout feature of this home is the popular main floor bonus room. Whether you require a home office, a cozy den, or a playroom for the little ones, this versatile space can adapt to suit your needs perfectly. As you embark on this exciting renovation journey, envision the incredible transformation that awaits. Create a space that reflects your unique style and personality while maximizing the potential of every square inch. The last 4 bedroom with this floor plan sold for 330k. You'll have instant equity
